  • public class AgentLauncherSelectorManagedScript
extends ResourceSelectorScript<AgentLauncher,​AgentLauncherSelectionContext>
    Extension of ResourceSelectorScript that delegates selection of a job's agent launcher when more than one choice is available. See also: AgentLauncherSelector.

    4.0.0
